<plot>This short documentary was first shown on the Turner Classic Movies (TCM) cable channel. Stuntmen specializing in various fields discuss their craft and explain the planning, execution, and safety aspects of the stunts they perform. The areas discussed include car chases, fistfights, sword fights, high work (e.g., jumping from high buildings or hanging from a tall ladder), and working with horses.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?063626</url></doc>
